definitions.definition: ( music ) The headlining band or performer at a concert or similar event; the best-known and first billed musician, comedian, etc., often performing as the final act of the evening .

main_definition: ( music ) The headlining band or performer at a concert or similar event; the best-known and first billed musician, comedian, etc., often performing as the final act of the evening .

definitions.definition: The interior fabric covering the roof of a vehicle .

main_definition: ( automotive ) The interior fabric covering the roof of a vehicle .
